    def test_auto_generated_employee_id(self, driver):
        print("\n>>> Test: Verify Auto-Generated Employee ID")
    
        # --- PAGE OBJECTS ---
        login_page = LoginPage(driver)
        dashboard_page = DashboardPage(driver)
        pim_page = PIMPage(driver)
        add_employee_page = AddEmployeePage(driver)
    
        # --- LOGIN ---
        login_page.login(Config.USERNAME, Config.PASSWORD)
        WebDriverWait(driver, 15).until(lambda d: dashboard_page.is_dashboard_displayed())
        assert dashboard_page.is_dashboard_displayed(), "⚠ Login failed"
    
        # --- NAVIGATE TO ADD EMPLOYEE ---
        dashboard_page.navigate_to_pim()
        WebDriverWait(driver, 15).until(lambda d: pim_page.is_pim_page())
        assert pim_page.is_pim_page(), "⚠ Failed to navigate to PIM"
    
        pim_page.navigate_to_add_employee()
        WebDriverWait(driver, 15).until(lambda d: add_employee_page.is_add_employee_page())
        assert add_employee_page.is_add_employee_page(), "⚠ Failed to navigate to Add Employee"
    
        # --- FILL EMPLOYEE DETAILS ---
        first_name = TestDataGenerator.generate_random_string(6)
        last_name = TestDataGenerator.generate_random_string(8)
        add_employee_page.fill_basic_employee_details(first_name, last_name)
    
        # --- READ AUTO-GENERATED EMPLOYEE ID ---
        EMPLOYEE_ID_INPUT = (By.ID, "employeeId")
